This paper is about inferring missing links in knowledge graphs using a probabilistic graphical model and variational inference. The paper focuses on a practical query answering task involving predicting the relation of a given entity pair. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Databases (cs.DB), and Information Retrieval (cs.IR).
